						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">It seems to me they had something like arrays defined with pre-determined patterns of pieces and probably had it periodically pick one of those out. I don't know how many arrays they would have had, but probably a lot to make it really feign randomness.</div>
